            <abstract>
                <p>Strelcyn reported in <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><citedRange unit="page">136</citedRange></bibl> 
                    that this prayer is against blacksmiths, among other things. Blacksmiths are usually referred to as 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነሃቢ፡</foreign>, while this text instead uses the term <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጠቢብ፡</foreign>, 
                    which can also have many other meanings, such as "wise man / scholar / physician / artisan / expert / craftsman".</p>
